<section class="doc-shell">
  <div class="section-heading">
    <p class="eyebrow">Embedded Monaco</p>
    <h2>Use the compiler and editor directly in lessons.</h2>
    <p class="lead">The website bundle exposes two helpers: a simple single-file editor for snippets and a multi-file workspace editor for richer tutorials.</p>
  </div>
